---
import Page from '../../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page
  title="Karaoke Lounge — Sing Your Heart Out | All Star Party World"
  description="Step up to the mic at All Star Party World's Karaoke Lounge. Professional mics, stage lighting, and thousands of songs. Available as a party add-on or standalone experience in Miami."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="kl-hero" aria-label="Karaoke Lounge hero">
    <div class="kl-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
      <img src="/karaoke-photos/karaoke-lounge-singing.jpg" alt="" />
      <div class="kl-hero-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="kl-hero-content">
      <div class="kl-eyebrow">Signature Experience</div>
      <h1 class="kl-hero-title">Karaoke<br /><span class="kl-accent">Lounge</span></h1>
      <p class="kl-hero-sub">Professional microphones. Stage lighting. A massive song library. All inside All Star Party World. Your guests don't just watch — they perform.</p>
      <div class="kl-hero-actions">
        <a href="/book" class="btn-primary">Add to Your Party</a>
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn-ghost">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="kl-hero-scroll" aria-hidden="true">
      <span>Scroll</span>
      <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Is It -->
  <section class="kl-what" aria-label="About the Karaoke Lounge">
    <div class="kl-what-inner">
      <div class="kl-what-image">
        <img src="/karaoke-photos/karaoke-lounge-group.jpg" alt="Group of young women singing on microphones in the All Star Party World karaoke lounge with stage lighting" />
        <div class="kl-image-badge" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="badge-icon"><i class="fas fa-microphone" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          <span class="badge-label">Live Stage</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="kl-what-text">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">The Experience</div>
        <h2>Your Own <span class="kl-accent">Stage Moment</span></h2>
        <p>The Karaoke Lounge puts your guests in the spotlight — literally. With professional-grade microphones, programmable stage lighting, and a song catalog spanning every genre and decade, every birthday kid, graduate, or party guest gets their pop star moment.</p>
        <p>Perfect for mixed-age parties. Kids and adults take turns at the mic while the party room vibes stay high.</p>
        <ul class="kl-feature-list" role="list">
          <li><span class="check-icon" aria-hidden="true">✦</span> Professional wireless microphones</li>
          <li><span class="check-icon" aria-hidden="true">✦</span> Stage-quality lighting rig</li>
          <li><span class="check-icon" aria-hidden="true">✦</span> Thousands of songs — all genres</li>
          <li><span class="check-icon" aria-hidden="true">✦</span> Dual screen display (performer + audience)</li>
          <li><span class="check-icon" aria-hidden="true">✦</span> All Star specialist on deck</li>
          <li><span class="check-icon" aria-hidden="true">✦</span> All ages welcome</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/book" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:1.5rem;display:inline-flex;">Book This Experience</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="kl-steps" id="how-it-works" aria-label="How the Karaoke Lounge works">
    <div class="kl-steps-inner">
      <div class="section-eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">How It Works</div>
      <h2 style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;">Pick a Song. <span class="kl-accent">Own the Stage.</span></h2>
      <div class="kl-steps-grid" role="list">
        <div class="kl-step" role="listitem">
          <div class="step-num" aria-hidden="true">01</div>
          <div class="step-icon" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fas fa-list-music"></i></div>
          <h3>Choose Your Song</h3>
          <p>Browse thousands of tracks on the digital song library. Pop, hip-hop, reggaeton, classics — if you know it, we probably have it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="kl-step" role="listitem">
          <div class="step-num" aria-hidden="true">02</div>
          <div class="step-icon" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fas fa-microphone-alt"></i></div>
          <h3>Grab the Mic</h3>
          <p>Step up, take the wireless mic, and let the stage lighting do its thing. The audience sees your lyrics on a big screen too.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="kl-step" role="listitem">
          <div class="step-num" aria-hidden="true">03</div>
          <div class="step-icon" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i></div>
          <h3>Take Your Bow</h3>
          <p>Finish to applause, pass the mic, and watch the next star perform. Add unlimited performances to your party session.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Add-On Banner -->
  <section class="kl-addon" aria-label="Add Karaoke Lounge to your party">
    <div class="kl-addon-inner">
      <div class="kl-addon-text">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">Party Add-On</div>
        <h2>Add It to Any Party Package</h2>
        <p>The Karaoke Lounge is available as a premium add-on to any All Star Party World package. Book it alongside your main party or as a standalone experience for smaller groups.</p>
        <p>Ask about karaoke-only bookings for evening events.</p>
        <a href="/book" class="btn-primary">Get a Quote</a>
      </div>
      <div class="kl-addon-details" role="list" aria-label="Details">
        <div class="detail-card" role="listitem">
          <i class="fas fa-clock" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <div>
            <strong>Duration</strong>
            <span>Open during your event</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-card" role="listitem">
          <i class="fas fa-users" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <div>
            <strong>Capacity</strong>
            <span>Unlimited performers</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-card" role="listitem">
          <i class="fas fa-child" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <div>
            <strong>Age Range</strong>
            <span>All ages welcome</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-card" role="listitem">
          <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <div>
            <strong>Location</strong>
            <span>Inside All Star Party World</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Other Experiences -->
  <section class="kl-more" aria-label="More signature experiences">
    <div class="kl-more-inner">
      <div class="section-eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">More Experiences</div>
      <h2 style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Stack the <span class="kl-accent">Fun</span></h2>
      <div class="kl-more-grid">
        <a href="/experiences/paint-me-one" class="more-card" aria-label="Paint Me One experience">
          <div class="more-card-icon" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fas fa-paint-brush"></i></div>
          <div class="more-card-content">
            <h3>Paint Me One</h3>
            <p>An immersive blacklight neon art studio. Kids paint glowing canvases they take home.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="more-card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/experiences/pop-star-divas" class="more-card" aria-label="Pop Star Divas experience">
          <div class="more-card-icon" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fas fa-crown"></i></div>
          <div class="more-card-content">
            <h3>Pop Star Divas</h3>
            <p>Glam makeup, diva costumes, and a full pop star photo shoot moment they'll never forget.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="more-card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/experiences/vr-experience" class="more-card" aria-label="VR Experience">
          <div class="more-card-icon" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fas fa-vr-cardboard"></i></div>
          <div class="more-card-content">
            <h3>VR Experience</h3>
            <p>Strap on a headset and step into another world. Racing, adventures, and more.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="more-card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="kl-cta" aria-label="Book the Karaoke Lounge">
    <div class="kl-cta-bg" aria-hidden="true">
      <img src="/karaoke-photos/karaoke-lounge-singing.jpg" alt="" />
      <div class="kl-cta-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="kl-cta-content">
      <h2>Ready to <span class="kl-accent">Perform?</span></h2>
      <p>Add the Karaoke Lounge to your next party at All Star Party World. We'll set the stage — you bring the voice.</p>
      <div class="kl-cta-actions">
        <a href="/book" class="btn-primary">Book Now</a>
        <a href="tel:+17864710100" class="btn-ghost">
          <i class="fas fa-phone" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          786-471-0100
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Page>

<style>
  :root {
    --kl-accent: #3B7DEB;
    --kl-glow: rgba(59,125,235,0.35);
  }
  .kl-accent { color: var(--kl-accent); }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--kl-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* ── Hero ── */
  .kl-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .kl-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .kl-hero-bg img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 20%;
  }
  .kl-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(8,9,16,0.94) 0%,
      rgba(8,9,16,0.75) 50%,
      rgba(59,125,235,0.15) 100%
    );
  }
  .kl-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 680px;
    padding: 8rem clamp(2rem, 8vw, 7rem) 6rem;
  }
  .kl-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--kl-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .kl-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 32px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--kl-accent);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .kl-hero-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 14vw, 11rem);
    line-height: 0.85;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 60px var(--kl-glow);
  }
  .kl-hero-title .kl-accent {
    display: block;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--kl-accent);
    color: transparent;
    text-shadow: 0 0 80px var(--kl-glow);
  }
  .kl-hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .kl-hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .kl-hero-scroll {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2.5rem; right: 3rem;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  }
  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px; height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent);
    animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes scrollPulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; }
    50% { opacity: 0.8; }
  }

  /* ── Buttons ── */
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--kl-accent);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(59,125,235,0.4), 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    transition: transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1), box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(59,125,235,0.6), 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }
  .btn-primary:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--kl-accent); outline-offset: 3px; }
  .btn-ghost {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1);
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { color: #fff; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-ghost:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5); outline-offset: 3px; }

  /* ── What ── */
  .kl-what { background: #0e0f14; padding: 7rem 2rem; }
  .kl-what-inner {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .kl-what-image {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .kl-what-image img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  .kl-image-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 1.5rem;
    left: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--kl-accent);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(59,125,235,0.5);
  }
  .badge-icon { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #fff; }
  .badge-label {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  }
  .kl-what-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .kl-what-text p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .kl-feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }
  .kl-feature-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  }
  .check-icon { color: var(--kl-accent); font-size: 0.65rem; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* ── Steps ── */
  .kl-steps { background: #14161e; padding: 7rem 2rem; }
  .kl-steps-inner { max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .kl-steps-inner h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .kl-steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .kl-step {
    position: relative;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1);
  }
  .kl-step:hover { border-color: rgba(59,125,235,0.3); transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .step-num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(59,125,235,0.08);
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.5rem; right: 1rem;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .step-icon {
    width: 48px; height: 48px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(59,125,235,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59,125,235,0.2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--kl-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .kl-step h3 {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .kl-step p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  }

  /* ── Add-On ── */
  .kl-addon { background: #0e0f14; padding: 7rem 2rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
  .kl-addon-inner {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .kl-addon-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .kl-addon-text p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .kl-addon-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .detail-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .detail-card:hover { border-color: rgba(59,125,235,0.25); }
  .detail-card i { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--kl-accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
  .detail-card div { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.25rem; }
  .detail-card strong {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .detail-card span { font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }

  /* ── More ── */
  .kl-more { background: #14161e; padding: 7rem 2rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
  .kl-more-inner { max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .kl-more-inner h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .kl-more-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .more-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1), background 0.2s ease;
  }
  .more-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(59,125,235,0.3);
    background: rgba(59,125,235,0.05);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }
  .more-card:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--kl-accent); outline-offset: 3px; }
  .more-card-icon {
    width: 44px; height: 44px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(59,125,235,0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59,125,235,0.2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--kl-accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .more-card-content { flex: 1; }
  .more-card-content h3 {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .more-card-content p { font-size: 0.82rem; line-height: 1.6; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); }
  .more-card-arrow {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .more-card:hover .more-card-arrow { color: var(--kl-accent); transform: translateX(4px); }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .kl-cta {
    position: relative;
    padding: 8rem 2rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .kl-cta-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; }
  .kl-cta-bg img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center 20%; }
  .kl-cta-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: rgba(8,9,16,0.88); }
  .kl-cta-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .kl-cta-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .kl-cta-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .kl-cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
